heading: Surplus Food Donation platform
description: A full-stack Website built with React and Node.js. Features include user authentication, product management, Donation page, and payment integration.

heading: Indian Food Nutrition Predictor
description: A machine learning web application that predicts nutrition values (calories, protein, carbs, fat) for Indian foods using a RandomForestRegressor model

heading: Simple Game UI
